node.text:
🏆FINALS TODAY🏆
•
Today are the finals for July COTM with Cupcake and Nala going head to head!! Who has what it takes to win the COTM trophy? Let us know in the comments who you got!!
•
For those who don’t know how to vote on our story, click on our profile picture on the top left corner of our page to get to our story and then click on the name of the of the chonk you want to win. Good luck to all may the best chonk win🏆🎉

node.text:
🏆SEMI FINALS TODAY🏆
•
The semi finals are underway with four of the biggest chonks going head to head. These are two amazing match ups. It hurts to see some of our favorite chonks go home early, but there has to be a winner. Let us know in the comments who you think will be the two chonks going head to head in the finals tomorrow!
•
For those who don’t know how to vote on our story, click on our profile picture on the top left corner of our page to get to our story and then click on the name of the of the chonk you want to win. Good luck to all may the best chonk win🏆🎉

node.text:
Introducing the July Chonk of the Month bracket🏆 We have complied 16 chonks from the month of July and put them head to head. Each matchup will be decided off a 24 hour vote on our story. The winner will be put into the hall of fame as well as have their name in our bio for the next month and also have the official CotM trophy sent to their house! Please see below for the dates for each round. Today is the first round of July CotM! Head over to our story to vote for the chonk you think deserves to move on to the quarters!
•
Round 1: August 2 
Quarter finals: August 3
Semi-finals: August 4
Finals: August 5
Winner announced July 6 12pm EST.
•
For those who don’t know how to vote on our story, click on our profile picture on the top left corner of our page to get to our story and then click on the name of the of the chonk you want to win. Good luck to all may the best chonk win🏆🎉
